      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Heart of a Hero",
        "Client": "Fugen the Elder",
        "Description": "Hey, \u003CPL\u003E! There\u0027s\r\na deathmatch raging on in the Arena\r\nbetween a teeny-tiny Tigrex and\r\na dango-droppingly big Diablos! If\r\nyou can go over and quiet that racket\r\ndown, I\u0027ll give ya some new titles.\r\nSound good? Good! Now go get to it!",
